\c 25
\s Amadodana kaAbrahama kuKetura; ukufa kukaAbrahama
\p
\v 1 UAbrahama wasebuya wathatha umfazi, lebizo lakhe linguKetura.
\v 2 Wasemzalela uZimrani loJokishani loMedani loMidiyani loIshibaki loShuwa\x + 1 Lan. 1.32,33.\x*.
\v 3 UJokishani wasezala uShebha loDedani. Lamadodana kaDedani ayengamaAshuri lamaLetushi lamaLewumi.
\v 4 Amadodana-ke kaMidiyani ayengoEfa loEferi loHanoki loAbida loElidaha. Wonke la ngamadodana kaKetura.
\v 5 UAbrahama wasemupha uIsaka konke ayelakho\x + 24.36.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa kumadodana abafazi abancane uAbrahama ayelabo uAbrahama wawanika izipho; wawasusa kuIsaka indodana yakhe\x + 21.14.\x*, esaphila, \add wawasa\add* empumalanga elizweni lempumalanga\x + Hlu. 6.3.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Lezi-ke zinsuku zeminyaka yempilo kaAbrahama ayiphilayo, iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu.
\v 8 UAbrahama wasephela, wafa eseluphele kuhle emdala enele\x + 15.15.\x*, wabuthelwa ezizweni zakibo\x + 25.17; 35.29; 49.29,33.\x*.
\v 9 UIsaka loIshmayeli amadodana akhe basebemngcwaba\x + 35.29.\x* obhalwini lweMakaphela, esiqintini sikaEfroni indodana kaZohari umHethi, esiqondene leMamre,
\v 10 isiqinti uAbrahama asithenga ebantwaneni bakaHethi\x + 23.16; 50.13.\x*; lapho uAbrahama wangcwatshwa loSara umkakhe\x + 49.31.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi emva kokufa kukaAbrahama, uNkulunkulu wambusisa uIsaka indodana yakhe; uIsaka wasehlala emthonjeni iLahayi-Royi\x + 16.14; 24.62.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaIshmayeli
\p
\v 12 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zikaIshmayeli indodana kaAbrahama, uHagari umGibithekazi, incekukazi kaSara, amzalela uAbrahama\x + 16.15.\x*.
\v 13 La-ke ngamabizo amadodana kaIshmayeli\x + 1 Lan. 1.29-31.\x* ngamabizo awo njengokuzalwa kwawo; izibulo likaIshmayeli nguNebayothi, loKedari loAdibeli loMibisama
\v 14 loMishima loDuma loMasa,
\v 15 uHadadi loTema, uJeturi, uNafishi loKedema;
\v 16 la ngamadodana kaIshmayeli, njalo la ngamabizo awo ngemizana yawo langemizi yawo, iziphathamandla ezilitshumi lambili\x + 17.20.\x* ngezizwe zawo.
\v 17 Njalo le yiminyaka yempilo kaIshmayeli, iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa; wasephela, wafa, wabuthelwa ebantwini bakibo\x + 25.8.\x*.
\v 18 Basebehlala kusukela eHavila\x + 1 Sam. 15.7.\x* kusiya eShuri\x + 16.7; 20.1. Eks. 15.22.\x* ephambi kweGibithe, ekuhambeni usiya eAsiriya; wahlala\f + \fk wahlala: \fl Heb. \fq wawa.\f* phambi kobuso babafowabo bonke.
\s Ukuzalwa kukaEsawu loJakobe
\p
\v 19 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zikaIsaka indodana kaAbrahama; uAbrahama wazala uIsaka\x + Mat. 1.2.\x*.
\v 20 UIsaka wayeseleminyaka engamatshumi amane mhla ethatha uRebeka, indodakazi kaBethuweli\x + 22.23.\x* umSiriya wePadani-Arama\x + 28.2.\x*, udadewabo kaLabani\x + 24.29.\x* umSiriya, kuye abe ngumka\add khe\add*.
\v 21 UIsaka wasemlabhelela umkakhe eN\sc KOSI\sc*ni, ngoba wayeyinyumba; iN\sc KOSI\sc* yasilabheleka ngaye\x + 2 Sam. 21.14; 24.25. 1 Lan. 5.20. 2 Lan. 33.13. Ezra 8.23.\x*, kwaze kwathi uRebeka umkakhe wathatha isisu.
\v 22 Abantwana-ke babedubana ngaphakathi kwakhe; wasesithi: Uba kunjalo, kungani nginje? Wasesiyabuza\x + 1 Sam. 9.9.\x* iN\sc KOSI\sc*.
\v 23 IN\sc KOSI\sc* yasisithi kuye: Izizwe ezimbili zisesizalweni sakho\x + 17.16; 24.60.\x*, izizwe ezimbili zizakwehlukana emibilini yakho. Njalo esinye isizwe sizakuba lamandla kulesinye isizwe, futhi omkhulu uzakhonza omncinyane\x + 27.29,40. Roma 9.12.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Kwathi sezigcwalisekile insuku zakhe zokubeletha, khangela-ke, amaphahla esiswini sakhe.
\v 25 Kwasekuphuma owokuqala ebomvana, yena wonke enjengesembatho soboya\x + 27.11,16,23.\x*; ngakho bamutha ibizo lakhe uEsawu.
\v 26 Njalo emva kwalokho kwaphuma umfowabo, lesandla sakhe sibambelele esithendeni sikaEsawu\x + Hos. 12.3.\x*; basebebiza ibizo lakhe uJakobe\x + 27.36.\x*. LoIsaka wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha ekuzalweni kwabo.
\v 27 Abafana basebekhula; uEsawu-ke waba ngumzingeli ohlakaniphileyo\x + 27.3,5.\x*, umuntu weganga; loJakobe umuntu obekekileyo\x + 6.9. Jobe 1.1,8; 2.3. Hlab. 37.37.\x* ehlala emathenteni\x + Heb. 11.9.\x*.
\v 28 Njalo uIsaka wayemthanda uEsawu ngoba wadla\f + \fk wadla: \fl Heb. \fq inyama yenyamazana yayisemlonyeni wakhe.\f* inyama yenyamazana\x + 27.4.\x* \add yakhe\add*; kodwa uRebeka wathanda uJakobe\x + 27.6.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Kwathi uJakobe esephekile ukudla okuphekiweyo, kwasekufika uEsawu evela egangeni, ekhathele.
\v 30 UEsawu wasesithi kuJakobe: Ake ungivumele ngiginye kokubomvu lokho okubomvu, ngoba ngikhathele. Ngalokhu babiza ibizo lakhe \add ngokuthi\add* uEdoma\f + \fk uEdoma: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq okubomvu.\f*.
\v 31 UJakobe wasesithi: Ngithengisela lamuhla ilungelo lobuzibulo bakho.
\v 32 UEsawu wasesithi: Khangela, sengizakufa; njalo liyini kimi ilungelo lobuzibulo?
\v 33 UJakobe wasesithi: Funga kimi lamuhla. Wasefunga kuye, wathengisa ilungelo lobuzibulo bakhe kuJakobe\x + Heb. 12.16.\x*.
\v 34 UJakobe wasenika uEsawu isinkwa lokudla okuphekiweyo kwamalentili*; wasesidla wanatha, wasukuma wahamba; ngalokho uEsawu wadelela ilungelo lobuzibulo bakhe\x + Heb. 12.16.\x*.
